Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:14.23,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}柔らかな　月明かりが照らす 泡沫の雪影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:19.77,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悴んだ小さな手を合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:25.73,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透き通る町に微笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:31.14,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さやぐ時代を全て包み込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:37.44,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}唯 染まる夜に 解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.36,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り注ぐ白い花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.61,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心をそっと解いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:49.15,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手のひらで溶けて刹那を魅せる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.13,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仰ぐ藍空の彼方に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.36,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行く先の輝映して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:00.09,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}惑いも灯せば良い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.99,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}結んだ雪華よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:12.48,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いまに届けと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:14.23,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}柔和的月光映照出那短暫的雪影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:19.77,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}合上那凍僵的小手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:25.73,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}對著通徹的街道 露出甜美的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:31.14,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在痛苦之時包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:37.44,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僅僅在那被暈染的夜裡釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.36,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那從天而降潔白的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.61,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄的觸動著我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:49.15,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看到它在手中融化的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.13,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仰望著蒼穹的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.36,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}映照出未來的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:00.09,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也照亮我的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.99,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的雪之華
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:12.48,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在就想傳達到汝心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是黃昏色的布幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你看 夕陽的餘暉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這裡是後臺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}演完人偶劇之後的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}偷偷地 聊著天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在無人知曉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是詩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}應該差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要能被你擁入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使是滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:25.25,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)\pos(804,538)}第八章\N\N\h                『宛若無法逃脫的詛咒』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}曾經 我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可減緩詛咒執行的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}方法？ 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}奪走無辜之人的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 所以心中才留下了『喜歡』這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但卻有種很寂寞 無法抑制的想去追求的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯 薩文蕾提會一直剝奪所有者的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}並計算它的總量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當超過一定量的時候殺害器官就會發動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.06,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(749,665)}{\blur3}Killing Organ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為別人的戀情也可以發動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真愚蠢呢 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吸收他人的戀情 可以暫時地矇騙計量器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我本以為那孩子吸收他人的戀情 是為了和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要逃跑就好了 但他卻故意出現在你們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要交換身份的話就能混淆我們的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 還能使啟動延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 為什麼侷限於校內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是因為 只要不是青春期的強烈愛戀的話 就沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}於是 我們被完美地欺騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以為薩文蕾提逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而你們為了加深犯罪的存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還特意把我叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我作為薩文蕾提與你接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而薩文蕾提還在遠處望風 而這時突然闖入的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們為了解除詛咒而行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她為什麼知道是這樣卻還要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比起那種都不知道有沒有效果的延緩手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還是和我們一起解除詛咒更…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}居然說要解除詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對我和薩文蕾提來說 詛咒和戀愛毫無區別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果解除詛咒 那現在的這份感情會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}難道說解開詛咒 讓我們將這一切都當成一場騙局嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就算這份感情只是出於詛咒 我也不能就這麼捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為你是人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然我其實也不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喜歡和戀愛什麼的 這種人類的心情 是道理說不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我還有很多不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我說了什麼傷害了你的那顆心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗很怕燙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要不要也吃點仙貝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅現在也不會說不讓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我…我才不要 你別太得意了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}薩文蕾提她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}薩文蕾提說過的 菲雅是非常好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}欺騙她讓他覺得非常難過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還有 她希望有天可以對那個戴眼鏡的女孩子說聲抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}並沒有什麼特別的意義 我要說的就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是嗎 那傢伙說了這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼夜知 接下來要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣下去的話 什麼事情都解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗 我有話想和薩文蕾提說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}昨天我給了他手機 要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}差不多該讓我聽聽你的想法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錐霞 約定的時間到了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}差不多快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉同學 準備得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他們可是什麼都沒透露給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全被當成外人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}確實 真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼 薩文蕾提差不多快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不可能會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會來的 因為我說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果不來的話就殺了白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你搞什麼啊此葉 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}結果 人類變成怎樣都無所謂呢 道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 很遺憾 那孩子不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絕對會來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們對 白穗 做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}終於來了嗎 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和電話裡說得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為覺得太麻煩了 所以打算直接毀了你 讓一切都結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個人類就是為此而下的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這和約定的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在說什麼啊 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉 班長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為了一方而捨棄另一方這種事  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夜知 雖然很明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想要…毀掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好像已經快壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你藏著的猥瑣的東西都露出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你這猥瑣的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已經拼命想把白穗擁入懷中殺掉她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我明白的  我很明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是那麼的美麗 連我也想殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是『箱型恐懼』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.90,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(678,665)}Fear in Cube
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比你多幾十倍的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以使人們進入忘我的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}學著點吧 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}結論是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我接下來會殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}開心的殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後把已經毫無價值的櫻參白穗也一併殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}眼看著那樣漂亮的臉即將變得醜陋 流著淚大聲叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後求饒 失禁 最終步向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別想得逞 別想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絕對不會讓你殺了白穗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第十九號機關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抉式螺旋態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人體鑽孔機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}禍動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下一個就會在白穗身上挖洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絕不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吾以王權詔曰 一切仿造的人偶都將是吾之臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}服從吧 臣子們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真奇妙 實在是奇妙絕倫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你以為這樣做就能鹹魚翻身了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第十八號機關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伸式外框態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}艾克希特公爵之女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}禍動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還是不在你身上挖洞了 乾脆直接撕裂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直到你身體四散為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要這樣 請不要這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 別殺薩文蕾提 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 別殺薩文蕾提 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 求你了 不管什麼我都願意做 無論是什麼都願意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你別殺了他 求你了 別殺薩文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 要我做什麼都好  求你了 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}殺了我也好 不要殺薩文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎樣了 實現王權的完全人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.94,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(714,665)}Sovereignty Perfection Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不會讓你殺了她的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不願意吧 不願意是吧 非常不願意對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣的話你就在這裡喚醒你全部的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}釋放出你體內裝置的所有利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是你喜歡白穗的話 如果你愛上了他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果那就是詛咒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就請讓我見證這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最後絕殺就由你來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你應該知道要做些什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}顯殺交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}薩文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}薩文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我還以為再也不能和你相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很想抱著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然是詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是這確實是我發自內心的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 很想抱著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絕對不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要菲雅加入了隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼可愛戰鬥力就會猛增～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅沒關係的話 我倒是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}話說 理事長在叫我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}總 總之先告訴我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼是體育季啊 到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不好 這莫非是感情交流 文化交流？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個 簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像菲雅一樣可愛的女孩子們一起蹦蹦跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}讓大家感到幸福的活動～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蠢斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是渦奈的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 拜託了 小菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為了我們舞蹈組的勝利 來 先親一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘛 不過菲雅運動神經看似不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對啊 跳舞什麼的很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了 就照渦奈說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以放開我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明天就開始練習 在操場附近的游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然 我是抱著必勝的決心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我詛咒你 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為出現了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}體育季什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}體育季？ 那蠢活動有什麼有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗知道什麼是體育季嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當、當然知道 這是常識哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}常識…什麼？？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}請進 理事長在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼 我也應該向你道謝 春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小菲雅和此葉也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還有 白穗同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}關於這次的事情 我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}使學生昏迷這件事一定要有個懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 你的懲罰就是 以後都要來學校認真地學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就目前來講 你是我世界上最討厭的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}變態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被如此美麗的女性責備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對於有某些癖好的人來說 或許是一種幸福啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 接下來給你們看這的東西有兩個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第一個是人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以就安排給漸音做助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另一個是漸音的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們也知道她非常喜歡可愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愛著 LOVE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是可惜的是 這些都不適合他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 作為代替 就讓…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}理事長 茶已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼 請把那些扯淡的事情都給忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}漸音 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}失 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原、原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}討厭 黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 漸音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 有個地方不能視而不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是、是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝招待我們吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一點我希望你能記住 你的父親非常重視你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼他要拖著病軀特意把薩文蕾提送到這裡來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想為你做一些事情而不惜做到這種程度 認同一點有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只因他太愚蠢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然我與他只是偶爾聊聊家常而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即便如此 有關於你的事情他也未曾不提過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 告訴你一件很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你曾經因為媽媽的推薦 而加入到一個非常有名的劇團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}據說 無論是誰都因你的演技而著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}倒沒什麼 我只是按照母親說的去做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你爸爸應該去看過你的表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是在最初的時候去過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爸爸 那個人對我不曾有過絲毫的關愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}並非如此 你爸爸曾勸說你媽媽讓你從劇團退出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想看見你真正的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他只是不善言語而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你只要記住這一點就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉同學 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 別在意 反正已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且還有認識的其他人偶 也被吸過精氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以非要說的話 也是習慣了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果無論如何都需要戀愛之心的話 請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會滿足你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想我已經沒問題了 但還是感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個是埋在我身上的 菲雅好像需要這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}送給你 當做謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}免罪符機構
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}詛咒本身還殘留著 只是失去了殺害器官而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:37.20,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(889,665)}Killing Organ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戀愛著 擁抱著 就是這種感覺喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一直都是這麼做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 不會輸給任何人的程度 從很久之前就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼啦 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知怎地想起了薩文蕾提和白穗的事情就…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}心裡感到騷動不安 即高興 又害羞 又羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是在理解以前不理解的事情的途中…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你先走吧 我有些事情要跟薩文蕾提說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}女生們的話題 懂了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}女生們的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望你能記住 你的父親非常重視你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 沒什麼 只是櫻參同學笑了 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 抱歉 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為你實在是太漂亮了 是緊張呢 還是有些怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果有什麼隔閡的話 就請直說吧 因為我不太擅長跟人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是、是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 像你這樣的人 我並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼 這樣我就獲得了櫻參同學『第一個朋友』的寶座了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像朋友那樣聊天吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個…這個… 話題… 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道前些日子在學校流傳的那件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果倒下的人被自己喜歡的那個人來探望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好像很快就能恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還有還有 啊 跟戀愛相關的我就單刀直入的問了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是說 男朋友之類的 有沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有個問題希望你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你能從我這裡吸取嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是說 是否菲雅身體裡面有或沒的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣啊 從結論上來說 也許存在 也許不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼 那不是沒意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那菲雅你的願望是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是希望有呢 還是希望沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個 只是想確認清楚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道 這個話題就結束了吧 結束了 你也給我忘掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}路漫漫其修遠兮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為了今後著想 給你個建議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也許年齡不一樣 重要的並不是時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會為你們兩個聲援的 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第九章 歸來者的某處不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不看就詛咒你哦
